Nadia Farès (Arabic, a mụrụ n'abalị 20 nke ọnwa Disemba afọ 1968 na Marrakech, Morocco) bụ onye obodo France na-eme ihe nkiri. O mere ihe nkiri izizi ya n'afọ 1992, na My Wife's Girlfriends Ọ ghọrọ onye a ma ama na akụkọ ndị uwe ojii Les Rivières pourpres (The Crimson Rivers)
Ọ pụtara dịka Jade Agent Kinler n'afọ 2007 action / thriller War, na dịka Pia na 2007 horror film Storm Warning
